snippet.title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
It's official! Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising releases worldwide on November 30, 2023! Preorder now!

Check out this fresh trailer featuring the new characters and fun game modes coming to GBVSR, such as Grand Bruise!

Preorder Here
https://rising.granbluefantasy.jp/en/products

Official GBVS Series Twitter
https://twitter.com/gbvs_official

#GranblueFantasyVersus #GBVS #GBVSR #Cygames
